{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0 Converts mono items on a track into a structured stereo take arrangement, emulating Pro Tools consolidation workflows.\par}
{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0 Automates Xenakios/SWS and REAPER actions to transform mono sources into properly formed stereo takes with preserved naming and colors.\par}

{\pard\ql\f0\sa180\li0\fi0\bullet\tx360\tab Selects all items on the current track.\par}
